title: "Steve Jobs" Actor Seth Rogen Not Much of a Techie
text:
"Steve Jobs" Actor Seth Rogen Not Much of a Techie Posted just a moment ago 
Universal (LOS ANGELES) -- Seth Rogen co-stars in the new movie Steve Jobs , but that doesn't make him a techie. 
While he plays Apple co-founder Steve Wozniak, you won't find him first in line for the latest iPhone. As he told ABC Radio, "I'm not that into apps, I use my phone for Twitter or s*** like that." 
He adds, "I'm not looking for more reasons to be on my phone or computer." 
In fact, Steve Jobs wasn't even really on Rogen's radar before he joined the cast of the movie. He admits, "I knew nothing about him before the movie. I was not particularly interested in him before the movie." 
Steve Jobs is in select theaters now, and is everywhere next week.
